android.car.storagemonitoring

类 IoStatsEntry.Metrics

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.storagemonitoring.IoStatsEntry.Metrics
  • 封闭类:
    IoStatsEntry

    public static final class IoStatsEntry.Metrics
extends java.lang.Object
    I/O activity metrics that pertain to either the foreground or the background state.

    • 字段概要

      字段 
      限定符和类型 字段和说明
      long bytesRead
      Total bytes that processes running on behalf of this user obtained via read() system calls.
      long bytesReadFromStorage
      Total bytes that processes running on behalf of this user obtained via read() system calls that actually were served by physical storage.
      long bytesWritten
      Total bytes that processes running on behalf of this user transferred via write() system calls.
      long bytesWrittenToStorage
      Total bytes that processes running on behalf of this user transferred via write() system calls that were actually sent to physical storage.
      static <any> CREATOR 
      long fsyncCalls
      Total number of fsync() system calls that processes running on behalf of this user made.
